			<h1>What is Duffel?</h1>
			<p>Duffel is a collaborative trip planning tool for DIY travelers. Tens of thousands of users are already using Duffel to plan their trips, and hundreds interact with us everyday.</p>
			<p>For destination sites, Duffel is an engaging and social marketing platform to promote your website content and destination. It is the most visual and interactive trip-planning-platform that is accessible to your visitors with one-click.</p>
			
			<h1>Is it free?</h1>
			<p>Yes! 100% free of charge.</p>
			
			<h1>Do I need to sign a contract?</h1>
			<p>Nope. You can stop using Duffel anytime you want, but your visitors may be hooked to it!</p>
			
			<h1>How to integrate?</h1>
			<p>Simply embed one line of HTML code and start engaging your visitors. See some examples and <a class="goodLink" href="/business/demo">how it works</a>.</p>
			
